# Emmy.earth - Automated Carbon Accounting Platform

## Project
Emmy.earth is a promotional website for an AI-powered carbon accounting platform that automates CO2 data collection and calculation for businesses.

## Tech Stack
- Static site generator: Jekyll
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (minimal)
- Styling: Tailwind 4, Custom CSS with CSS variables
- Components: SimpleLightbox for image galleries

